STATE of North Carolina
v.
Tracy R. INGRAM. No. 47P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2004. Tracy R. Ingram, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 2nd day of February 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Forsyth County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2004."
